  <ul>
  <li><a href="#sysmerge">Merging changed files via sysmerge(8)</a>
  <li><a href="#RmFiles">Files to delete and move</a>
  <li><a href="#Pkgup">Upgrading packages</a>
  </ul>
</ul>

